button</span></p><p class="Normal p_53A128ED"><span class="s_BDAA7F8C">2)</span><span class="s_E97E96B4"> </span><span class="s_BDAA7F8C">Each time you perceive</span><span class="s_E97E96B4"> a new sensation</span><span class="s_BDAA7F8C">, click on the corresponding button.</span><br /><span class="s_BDAA7F8C">&nbsp; button.</span></p><p class="Normal p_53A128ED"><span class="s_BDAA7F8C">4) Score how much you like this chocolate </span><span class="s_E97E96B4">right now.</span></p><p class="Normal p_53A128ED"><span class="s_BDAA7F8C">5) Repeat steps 1) to 4) for each of the 2 pieces of the sample.</span></p><p class="Normal p_53A128ED"><span class="s_BDAA7F8C">6) Rinse your mouth, relax and be prepared to evaluate the next sample in the same way.</span></p></body></html>" Events="[]" IsModal="false" StartWithChronometer="false" PlaySound="false" ScrollViewerVisible="true" Canvas.ZIndex="999" xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation" Canvas.Left="25.751" Canvas.Top="19.428" />
